title: Four-Player Skirmishes
type: text/vnd.tiddlywiki

The “Hoth Battlefield” skirmish map, found on the Skirmish Map Sheet, allows four players to compete in a massive Imperial Assault battle. Depending on which mission is played, the players could all compete against each other in a Free-For-All or in a Team Battle.